Shirakawa Says Rapid Yen Surge Risks Lasting Damage to Economy

-- B y   A k i   I t o
-- 
2011-10-07T07:34:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/shirakawa-says-rapid-yen-surge-risks-lasting-damage-to-economy.html
Bank of Japan (8301)  Governor Masaaki
Shirakawa said the yen’s rapid surge risks exacting lasting
damage to  Japan ’s economy and could speed up the move of
companies overseas. Shirakawa spoke at a news conference in
 Tokyo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
